reviews.title: Issue with Wallpaper NOT Changing with Profile
reviews.comment: I have attempted to reach you by email and after my third attempt in the last day have had no reply. Recently I have had an issue where when I change my profile (activate) it does not change the wallpaper as configured. If I activate the profile a second time it does change the wallpaper. I have remove the app, put it back, created new profiles, nothing changes this behaviour. If I can get an answer I will change to 5 stars and buy the paid version gladly.   Droid Razr Maxx HD 4.1 JB.
reviews.author: Mario Cipriano

reviews.title: Didnt do whst I needed
reviews.comment: Its a real shame this looked really nice but when I set up a profile ni matter what I tried I couldn\'t get the notification tone to go silent whilst still having the ring tone on
reviews.author: James Forsyth

reviews.title: Good
reviews.comment: Its a good app..  Worked mostly. Changes profile automatically 80% of the times.. However some times it doesnt automatically..  I guess its because of low network coverage. Would appreciate help on that.  Otherwise a great app.  Works even without the need for gps. Lot of customisation options.  Like it. Thanks for keepibg it free.
reviews.author: Shreyas Kotian

reviews.title: Great
reviews.comment: I use it since my first Android\'s phone. Great software. Thanks
reviews.author: Herman Aksara

reviews.title: Location doesn\'t work
reviews.comment: When I\'m at home, it thinks I\'m at work and when I\'m at work it thinks I\'m home.  76 miles apart.  It requires me to reboot the phone while all other GPS-based apps update properly.  Glad I didn\'t pay!
reviews.author: Kiera NaLavin

reviews.title: It is very easy to use
reviews.comment: I like the app a lot and is very well designed for easy use, however, it doesn\'t change profile according to location. I\'ve also wrote to the developer and no answer, so I suppose it has just the feature but not the function. Otherwise, I would rate it a 5 star.
reviews.author: Liviu Singher

reviews.title: Awesome!!
reviews.comment: Love being able to put my phone in to a Sleep profile automatically!! I have Audio Manager Pro, and I have a Sleep profile in that app that I\'ve made. With MyProfiles though, my phone will go to a Sleep profile automatically(in case I fall asleep before setting this profile on my phone)! I don\'t even bother with the profile in Audio Manager Pro anymore, why bother when this app will do the same thing automatically! LOVE this app! My only complaint is I didn\'t find it sooner! What\'s not to love about??!!
reviews.author: Mike Chapman

reviews.title: Splendid
reviews.comment: I had some troubles with the 3g, as I was unable to reactivate it no matter what I tried. However after reinstalling the app, everything works fine. It is really nice feature to automatically switch profiles based on the operator cells nearby and wireless networks available.
reviews.author: Vassil Lazzarrov

reviews.title: Rules no longer function
reviews.comment: Sadly after using for 6 months a recent update has caused the program to cease following rules.
reviews.author: Michael Gettys

reviews.title: As good as competitor
reviews.comment: There are bug on competitor \"ProfileScheduler\" on my Xperia S. This is as good as it. But one thing to improve, please separate the ring volume and notification volume. I would mute/minimize the notification volume such as whatsapp/sms/facebook but keep my ring volume as high as possible for receiving emergency call when i am sleeping.
reviews.author: Axel Leung

reviews.title: Awsome app...
reviews.comment: Hi All,  I am proudly say now that I have \"Smart Phone\".   Recently I am back to ICS from JB to save RAM... I have been looking this amazing App and \"Profile Manager\" has solved it all...  5 star because of its unique feature which combines Location with adjacent cell...  Even people who can\'t buy this app can use it with full functionality as it offers \"Three Rules\" at times... which is enough for normal users.  Love this app.... All the best and enjoy \"Smart Phone\".
reviews.author: Dakshesh Bohra

reviews.title: Good appl.
reviews.comment: Thank you for the good application it does what it says and much more hat rise for developers 5 stars is a must. HTC ONE X
reviews.author: Yasser Dafrawy

reviews.title: Been using for over a year
reviews.comment: I love this app. The only thing I missed from my BlackBerry was the different profiles. I wish I could adjust different notifications independently, but it\'s the best profile app that I have found.
reviews.author: Terry Magill

reviews.title: Easy-to-use and it works !
reviews.comment: Use it to change sound volume based on time and day of week, and also by location.  Wished it had more profile icons (speaker, mute, briefcase - things that most people use this app for).  But other than that, it works fine.
reviews.author: Mais S

reviews.comment: Looks great working great.
reviews.author: Nitsan Dodo

reviews.title: Very handy
reviews.comment: Lot of different rule options and the best of all everything works :-)
reviews.author: Sankar Nair

reviews.title: Mind your battery
reviews.comment: Good but it drains your battery. It worths 5 stars if it consumes much less battery.
reviews.author: William Law

reviews.title: Works on Note 2 LTE
reviews.comment: It switched as it should on wifi disconnect/connect and did everything I wanted except for perhaps adding multiple conditions on a rule. At least I can have a time period combined with wifi connection, and in theory you could create multiple rules but I suspect that this would get messy after a while. Some kind of \"work\" or \"office\" icon would be nice... I couldn\'t find anything that really represents my workplace profile (a briefcase or dollar sign or something?) Great app, and after a couple more days of testing I think i\'ll buy the pro version to show my support!
reviews.author: Steve Rand

reviews.title: The profile manager does not work always for exception groups.
reviews.comment: If it works properly then the volume becomes mute. Please remove the bug

reviews.comment: I have an Idea For You .That is When 3 Missed Call Placed From A Person/Number Then Profile change Automatically To General/Silent/Vibration. I Hope This Feature Can be Added In Update Version and i waiting for this.
